      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 299230.0,
      "end_time": 300452.0,
      "text": "Thank you!"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 300476.0,
      "end_time": 304870.0,
      "text": "(Applause continues)"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 305203.0,
      "end_time": 306378.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 307616.0,
      "end_time": 312000.0,
      "text": "Like the speaker before me -- I am a TED virgin, I guess."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 312322.0,
      "end_time": 315254.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m also the first time here, and ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 315278.0,
      "end_time": 316399.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 316423.0,
      "end_time": 317684.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t know what to say!"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 317708.0,
      "end_time": 321141.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 321165.0,
      "end_time": 323976.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m really happy that Mr. Anderson invited me."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 324000.0,
      "end_time": 327000.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m really grateful that I get a chance to play for everyone."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 327523.0,
      "end_time": 330794.0,
      "text": "And the song that I just played was by Josef Hofmann."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 330818.0,
      "end_time": 332667.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s called \"Kaleidoscope.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 332691.0,
      "end_time": 339354.0,
      "text": "And Hofmann is a Polish pianist and composer of the late 19th century,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 339378.0,
      "end_time": 342649.0,
      "text": "and he&#39;s widely considered one of the greatest pianists of all time."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 343173.0,
      "end_time": 345705.0,
      "text": "I have another piece that I&#39;d like to play for you."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 345729.0,
      "end_time": 349772.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s called \"Abegg Variations,\" by Robert Schumann,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 349796.0,
      "end_time": 352637.0,
      "text": "a German 19th-century composer."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 353994.0,
      "end_time": 358145.0,
      "text": "The name \"Abegg\" is actually A-B-E-G-G,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 358169.0,
      "end_time": 360111.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s the main theme in the melody."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 360136.0,
      "end_time": 362635.0,
      "text": "(Plays the notes A, B, E, G and G)"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 364700.0,
      "end_time": 367772.0,
      "text": "That comes from the last name of one of Schumann&#39;s female friends."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 368673.0,
      "end_time": 370446.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 370470.0,
      "end_time": 372573.0,
      "text": "But he wrote that for his wife."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 372597.0,
      "end_time": 375974.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 376715.0,
      "end_time": 378541.0,
      "text": "So actually, if you listen carefully,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 378565.0,
      "end_time": 381553.0,
      "text": "there are supposed to be five variations on this Abegg theme."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 381986.0,
      "end_time": 384590.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s written around 1834,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 384614.0,
      "end_time": 386890.0,
      "text": "so even though it&#39;s old, I hope you&#39;ll like it."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 390583.0,
      "end_time": 395976.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 799987.0,
      "end_time": 801987.0,
      "text": "(Music ends)"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 803312.0,
      "end_time": 810171.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 810748.0,
      "end_time": 812352.0,
      "text": "Now comes the part that I hate."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 815591.0,
      "end_time": 818470.0,
      "text": "Well, because Mr. Anderson told me"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 818710.0,
      "end_time": 820948.0,
      "text": "that this session is called \"Sync and Flow,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 820972.0,
      "end_time": 823968.0,
      "text": "I was wondering, \"What do I know that these geniuses don&#39;t?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 823993.0,
      "end_time": 825160.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 825184.0,
      "end_time": 827309.0,
      "text": "So, I&#39;ll talk about musical composition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 827333.0,
      "end_time": 829314.0,
      "text": "even though I don&#39;t know where to start."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 830679.0,
      "end_time": 832000.0,
      "text": "How do I compose?"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 832544.0,
      "end_time": 836550.0,
      "text": "I think Yamaha does a really good job of teaching us how to compose."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 836452.0,
      "end_time": 840139.0,
      "text": "What I do first is, I make a lot of little musical ideas"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 840163.0,
      "end_time": 842354.0,
      "text": "you can just improvise here at the piano --"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 842378.0,
      "end_time": 846950.0,
      "text": "and I choose one of those to become my main theme, my main melody,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 846119.0,
      "end_time": 848000.0,
      "text": "like the Abegg that you just heard."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 848300.0,
      "end_time": 851801.0,
      "text": "And once I choose my main theme, I have to decide:"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 851826.0,
      "end_time": 855168.0,
      "text": "Out of all the styles in music, what kind of style do I want?"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 855628.0,
      "end_time": 858219.0,
      "text": "And this year, I composed a Romantic style."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 858568.0,
      "end_time": 862444.0,
      "text": "So for inspiration, I listened to Liszt and Tchaikovsky"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 862469.0,
      "end_time": 864444.0,
      "text": "and all the great Romantic composers."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 864960.0,
      "end_time": 870000.0,
      "text": "Next, I make the structure of the entire piece with my teachers."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 870443.0,
      "end_time": 872388.0,
      "text": "They help me plan out the whole piece."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 872412.0,
      "end_time": 876114.0,
      "text": "And then the hard part is filling it in with musical ideas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 876138.0,
      "end_time": 878112.0,
      "text": "because then you have to think."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 878136.0,
      "end_time": 879909.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 879933.0,
      "end_time": 883412.0,
      "text": "And then, when the piece takes somewhat of a solified form --"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 883436.0,
      "end_time": 885658.0,
      "text": "solidified, excuse me -- solidified form,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 885682.0,
      "end_time": 890708.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re supposed to actually polish the piece, polish the details,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 890732.0,
      "end_time": 894000.0,
      "text": "and then polish the overall performance of the composition."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 894843.0,
      "end_time": 897887.0,
      "text": "And another thing that I enjoy doing is drawing."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 897912.0,
      "end_time": 901396.0,
      "text": "Drawing, because I like to draw, you know, Japanese anime art."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 901420.0,
      "end_time": 903703.0,
      "text": "I think that&#39;s a craze among teens right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 904385.0,
      "end_time": 906370.0,
      "text": "And once I realized it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 906610.0,
      "end_time": 910570.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s a parallel between creating music and creating art,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 910810.0,
      "end_time": 915191.0,
      "text": "because for your motive, or your little initial idea for your drawing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 915215.0,
      "end_time": 918183.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s your character -- you want to decide who you want to draw,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 918207.0,
      "end_time": 920363.0,
      "text": "or if you want to draw an original character."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 920387.0,
      "end_time": 923883.0,
      "text": "And then you want to decide: How are you going to draw the character?"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 923908.0,
      "end_time": 927320.0,
      "text": "Like, am I going to use one page? Am I going to draw it on the computer?"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 927344.0,
      "end_time": 930520.0,
      "text": "Am I going to use a two-page spread like a comic book?"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 930544.0,
      "end_time": 932747.0,
      "text": "For a more grandiose effect, I guess."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 933131.0,
      "end_time": 936278.0,
      "text": "And then you have to do the initial sketch of the character,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 936302.0,
      "end_time": 938340.0,
      "text": "which is like your structure of a piece,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 938364.0,
      "end_time": 942124.0,
      "text": "and then you add pen and pencil, and whatever details that you need --"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 942148.0,
      "end_time": 943644.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s polishing the drawing."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 944250.0,
      "end_time": 947747.0,
      "text": "And another thing that both of these have in common is your state of mind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 947771.0,
      "end_time": 952757.0,
      "text": "because I know I&#39;m one of those teenagers that are really easily distracted."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 952781.0,
      "end_time": 957795.0,
      "text": "So if I&#39;m trying to do homework and I don&#39;t feel like it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 957820.0,
      "end_time": 960573.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll try to draw or, you know, waste my time."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 960999.0,
      "end_time": 963777.0,
      "text": "And then what happens is, sometimes I absolutely can&#39;t draw"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 963801.0,
      "end_time": 965762.0,
      "text": "or I can&#39;t compose at all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 965786.0,
      "end_time": 968920.0,
      "text": "and then it&#39;s like there&#39;s too much on your mind."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 968116.0,
      "end_time": 970492.0,
      "text": "You can&#39;t focus on what you&#39;re supposed to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 970517.0,
      "end_time": 975818.0,
      "text": "And sometimes, if you manage to use your time wisely and work on it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 975842.0,
      "end_time": 978931.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ll get something out of it, but it doesn&#39;t come naturally."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 979486.0,
      "end_time": 981970.0,
      "text": "What happens is, if something magical happens,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 981994.0,
      "end_time": 984598.0,
      "text": "if something natural happens to you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 984622.0,
      "end_time": 988241.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re able to produce all this beautiful stuff instantly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 988265.0,
      "end_time": 990393.0,
      "text": "and then that&#39;s what I consider \"flow,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 990417.0,
      "end_time": 994385.0,
      "text": "because that&#39;s when everything clicks and you&#39;re able to do anything."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 994409.0,
      "end_time": 998170.0,
      "text": "You feel like you&#39;re on top of your game and you can do anything you want."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 998194.0,
      "end_time": 1001415.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not going to play my own composition today because,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 1001440.0,
      "end_time": 1004001.0,
      "text": "although I did finish it, it&#39;s way too long."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 1005500.0,
      "end_time": 1008238.0,
      "text": "Instead, I&#39;d like to try something called \"improvisation.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 1008260.0,
      "end_time": 1010481.0,
      "text": "I have here seven note cards,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 1010510.0,
      "end_time": 1013692.0,
      "text": "one with each note of the musical alphabet."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 1013710.0,
      "end_time": 1017593.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;d like someone to come up here and choose five --"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 1017620.0,
      "end_time": 1019608.0,
      "text": "anyone to come up here and choose five --"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 1019630.0,
      "end_time": 1022342.0,
      "text": "and then I can make it into some sort of melody,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 1022370.0,
      "end_time": 1023750.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;ll improvise it."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 1024710.0,
      "end_time": 1027841.0,
      "text": "Wow. A volunteer, yay!"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 1027869.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1029342.9999999999,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 1029359.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1032485.9999999999,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 1032510.0,
      "end_time": 1034122.0,
      "text": "Jennifer Lin: Nice to meet you."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 1034630.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1037617.0000000001,
      "text": "Goldie Hawn: Thank you. Choose five?"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 1037640.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1039701.0000000001,
      "text": "JL: Yes, five cards. Any five cards."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 1039730.0,
      "end_time": 1041296.0,
      "text": "GH: OK, one. JL: OK."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 1042190.0,
      "end_time": 1043760.0,
      "text": "GH: Two. JL: Yes."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 1045250.0,
      "end_time": 1046176.0,
      "text": "GH: Three."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 1048900.0,
      "end_time": 1050508.0,
      "text": "GH: Oh, D and F -- too familiar."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 1050530.0,
      "end_time": 1055138.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 1055170.0,
      "end_time": 1058506.0,
      "text": "JL: One more. GH: OK. \"E\" for \"effort.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 1058530.0,
      "end_time": 1061801.0,
      "text": "JL: Would you mind reading them out in the order that you chose them?"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 1061820.0,
      "end_time": 1068110.0,
      "text": "GH: OK -- C, G, B, A and E."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 1068140.0,
      "end_time": 1069294.0,
      "text": "JL: Thank you very much!"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 1069310.0,
      "end_time": 1071286.0,
      "text": "GH: You&#39;re welcome. And what about these?"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 1071310.0,
      "end_time": 1073836.0,
      "text": "JL: I won&#39;t use them. Thank you!"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 1075200.0,
      "end_time": 1081457.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 1082150.0,
      "end_time": 1085528.0,
      "text": "Now, she chose C, G, B, A, E."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 1085550.0,
      "end_time": 1087970.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to try to put that in some sort of order."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 1088000.0,
      "end_time": 1091512.0,
      "text": "(Plays notes)"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 1093610.0,
      "end_time": 1095348.0,
      "text": "OK, that&#39;s nice."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 1096360.0,
      "end_time": 1097973.0,
      "text": "So, I&#39;m going to have a moment to think,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 1098000.0,
      "end_time": 1100242.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;ll try to make something out of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 1105130.0,
      "end_time": 1108378.0,
      "text": "(Plays the five notes)"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 1116440.0,
      "end_time": 1122897.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 1312200.0,
      "end_time": 1314201.0,
      "text": "(Music ends)"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 1314230.0,
      "end_time": 1321404.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
